@startuml form-script-lifecycle
title Form Script (DSL) Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : YAML definition authored (.forms.yaml)

Draft --> Validated : Passed CLI / Schema Validation
Validated --> Imported : Imported to Tenant Registry

Imported --> Active : Version Promoted for Use
Imported --> Deprecated : Replaced by Newer Build
Deprecated --> Archived : Historical Reference

@enduml
